latestPosts.caption:
‼️DIWALI GIVEAWAY ‼️
Please read the entire caption carefully.

Finally doing my first ever giveaway, a small token of appreciation for all the love and support you shower on me and to celebrate how far we’ve come in this incredible and creative journey ❤️

There will be 3 winners!
The hampers are curated on the basis of different skin tones and skin types. Please mention the following codes in your comments so that I can build you a hamper that’s specifically designed to suit your skin in the best way possible.

Skin type:
Combination-C, Normal-N, Dry-D
Skin tones:
Deep-d, Medium-m, Light-l
 
Eg- if you’ve combination and deep skin, add “Cd” at the end of your comment 🤍

Rules to enter the giveaway 
1. Follow @parnika_tomar on IG and save this post
2. Share this post on your story and tag me (take a screenshot of the story if your account is private) OR send this post to 3 people over DMs and send me a screenshot of the DMs
3. Like this post, tag 2 friends in the comments and compliment them. 

✨Brownie points if you: 
Share any other post/reel of mine that you like on your story and tag me (take a screenshot the story if your account is private)

Winners will be announced on 2nd November on my IG stories.

Good luck and have a very happy diwali! 🪔✨❤️
